  "description": "A DiscordSRV Extension that gives you a Linked rank! 🔗",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/linkedrank\">\n    <img alt=\"modrinth\" height=\"32\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_vector.svg\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/uhalexz/linkedrank\">\n    <img alt=\"github-singular\" height=\"32\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/social/github-singular_vector.svg\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<table align=\"center\">\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n      <img alt=\"example-linking\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/67da1062d9fed8807a67be9bc8139214e610c41b.png\">\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n\n---\n\n## 🔗 Linked Rank\n\nThis is a simple to use addon for DiscordSRV that automatically gives your players a \"Linked\" rank on your Minecraft server! 🔥\n\n---\n\n## 📦 Dependencies\n\n> Required to run this smoothly:\n\n- [LuckPerms](https://luckperms.net/) (handles permissions/ranks)\n- [DiscordSRV](https://discordsrv.com/) (handles discord linking)\n",
